Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.58,0:00:12.09,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}青ざめた町並
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.22,0:00:15.84,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}搖れる僕の影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.88,0:00:24.12,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}鈍い足取りは　行く先を知らず
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:30.00,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}交わせぬ　想い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.06,0:00:38.47,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君の瞳の中　映し出すものを
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.59,0:00:42.13,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}受け止める為に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.19,0:00:46.42,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}走り出していた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.76,0:00:52.15,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}差し出す　その手を
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:01:00.89,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ほどけないように　握り返す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.07,0:01:08.31,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}半分の月の夜は　僕らを照らして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.41,0:01:15.78,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}追いかけて來た時間を　僕は振り切って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.87,0:01:26.77,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}半分ずつの僕らは　描く先までも　見える
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.58,0:00:12.09,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}染成一片蔚藍的街道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.22,0:00:15.84,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我徘徊的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.88,0:00:24.12,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}拖著沉重的腳步不知該往何方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:30.00,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無法交織的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.06,0:00:38.47,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}為了接受在你眼中倒映出來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.59,0:00:42.13,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.19,0:00:46.42,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我飛奔出去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.76,0:00:52.15,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}絕不放開你伸出的雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:01:00.89,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我緊緊將其握住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.07,0:01:08.31,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夜晚半月的光輝映照著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.41,0:01:15.78,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我擺脫那追逐不休的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.87,0:01:26.77,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}半成熟的我們知道該如何描繪人生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.35,0:22:48.22,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ねぇ　指先であなたを感じて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.36,0:23:00.84,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ねぇ　あなたと見ていたこの景色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.33,0:23:13.62,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伝わる　優しさに身をゆだねて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.19,0:23:25.25,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}永遠など無い　わかっていたつもりだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.62,0:23:34.41,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}名前を呼ぶ　あなたの聲を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.56,0:23:40.40,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}胸の奧に　しまっておくから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.59,0:23:46.39,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}開かれた　扉の向こう側で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.58,0:23:53.10,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}こぼれぬように　消えないように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.35,0:22:48.22,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我還記得  指尖傳來的你的觸感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.36,0:23:00.84,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}還記得嗎  這與你一同眺望的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.33,0:23:13.62,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我寄身於你對我的這份溫柔之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.19,0:23:25.25,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我相信我已經看透了世上沒有永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.62,0:23:34.41,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你呼喚我的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.56,0:23:40.40,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我一直深埋心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.59,0:23:46.39,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}為了能在敞開的門那一側
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.58,0:23:53.10,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}永不流失  永不消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:02:01.68,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(680,355)}{\fad(0,900)}停滯的一分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.72,0:01:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙手礙腳的  給我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.07,0:01:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去外面等等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.59,0:01:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有情況的話  我會馬上通知你的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.40,0:01:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.69,0:01:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的情況指的是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香她…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.21,0:02:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香她怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.25,0:02:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算是穩定下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.49,0:02:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經很久沒有這樣發作了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那她得救了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.33,0:02:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉強算吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戎崎  為什麼你會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣的傢伙為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你故意來惹人嫌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.93,0:02:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  你是來惹我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香的情況怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.36,0:02:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手術或許會延期吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.37,0:02:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,36.3度  沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說要我戒煙…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼送我打火機啊  小夜子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  這裡是夏目家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是吾郎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.35,0:03:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜子  你正在睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  春天那麼暖和 沒辦法的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難為你老公正在這裡忙死忙活的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟在白天打盹  架子不小啊  太太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.97,0:03:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼是誰給吾郎做飯吃的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房間總是那麼整潔  又是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妖精悄悄地幫忙的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位妖精真了不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  好像還很可愛喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊  小夜子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能幫你爭取到一分鐘的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.92,0:04:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爭取？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現了的話我也會倒霉的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一  你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.91,0:04:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞希子說她只能爭取到這一分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.26,0:04:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真短呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一分鐘…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:04:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.37,0:05:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  真好…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間已經到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見  裕一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不趕快的話…就對不住谷崎小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:05:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生  這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:05:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是香煙形巧克力啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:05:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要吸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預定沒變  週末我會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩下大概一分鐘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一分鐘嗎  也可以在一分鐘結束後再投上10元哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.43,0:06:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你可能會比較忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說吾郎也是醫生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.71,0:06:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜子  你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.19,0:06:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心臟  跳得很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種奇怪的感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.64,0:06:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太太的心臟不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:06:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次雖然不太嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:07:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但想要完全恢復恐怕很困難
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍惜現在的時光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說這是香煙形巧克力…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才怪！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為  我把它和巧克力弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想遠走高飛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.54,0:08:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是裕一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美沙子小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  谷崎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.02,0:08:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.42,0:08:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生  您還是去繼續安歇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經睡醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  那還真是可惜呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用那種口氣說話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為嘛  醫生和護士的立場…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先找茬的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:08:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？我只是在說話而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:09:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真有一手啊  真幽默啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不賴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豬雜定食買回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩  戎崎是不是又跑出去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才在九-23號附近有輛外國車擦身而過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到挺像的男生坐在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外國車？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看錯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開車的還是個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.62,0:09:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃出醫院沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很糟嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞希子會生氣麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會非常地生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怕呢  亞希子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也狠狠地嘗過她三次重拳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.86,0:09:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.80,0:09:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是動真格的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體都被打飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被抓住的話會很生氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:09:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:09:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要遠走高飛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是順便去一下我家而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  去一下下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.16,0:10:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把門鎖好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.80,0:10:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一會繼續升學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.47,0:10:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東京？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時…還不確定  但有此打算
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去過東京
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡做模特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模特？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.67,0:10:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但因為父親的病而回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是獨生女  所以必須由我來照顧他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是遇到一些無聊的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可也無可奈何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.37,0:11:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也不會來安慰你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,0:11:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你志向很高遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我過去非常討厭這座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該能明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是…非常討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(432,440)}{\fs28}{\bord1}{\shad0}美沙子  給我滾出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(432,440)}{\fs28}{\bord1}{\shad0}你能聽見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(432,440)}{\fs28}{\bord1}{\shad0}滾出來  美沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(432,440)}{\fs28}{\bord1}{\shad0}喂  美沙子！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(432,440)}{\fs28}{\bord1}{\shad0}給我適可而止  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(432,440)}{\fs28}{\bord1}{\shad0}你聽見了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(432,440)}{\fs28}{\bord1}{\shad0}美沙子！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞希子…小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.55,0:12:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從以前開始直覺就很厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正鎖上了  要繼續嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.54,0:12:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戎崎  回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別給我開口啊  臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想給自己找借口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.81,0:13:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果一古腦兒全說了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣只會給女人添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要騙人 就給我騙到底
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.46,0:13:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是敢向里香吐露半個字  我就宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為夏目醫生會是個正經人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正經才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你怎麼看都是對太太一心一意嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說  太沉重了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.61,0:13:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.68,0:13:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天還真是糟糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.55,0:14:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算做什麼不關我事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢  谷崎所說的一定要遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓里香知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對身體肯定會有影響的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.36,0:14:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你騙誰 你知道個鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會是你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.29,0:14:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.69,0:14:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍛煉手指的靈活性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為里香要動手術了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次發作得太厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們開始考慮延期的必要性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但拖延也會帶來發作更加激烈的風險
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況太微妙了 到底該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.00,0:14:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這個專家也拿不定主意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果交由里香的母親去判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:15:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是她問了里香  問她怎麼打算
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.72,0:15:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後里香說 「我要動手術」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要活下去所以要動手術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認識她 已經是她小學時代的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直都是那種性格 表面愛逞強 內心卻很脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.66,0:15:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頑固的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.01,0:15:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次真是讓我感動到要哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭一次聽她說  聽她說她想要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭一次聽她說…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相機不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦！怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.66,0:15:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膠片卷不動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.35,0:15:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有把膠捲好好放進去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.21,0:15:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然有放進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.31,0:15:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別騙人了  你肯定沒有弄好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.09,0:15:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果卷第一張時沒對準的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:16:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膠卷就會這樣在中途卡住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.15,0:16:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.99,0:16:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戎崎君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.18,0:16:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人找你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  是美雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  送給那女孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.81,0:16:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是制服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.35,0:16:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.45,0:16:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是姐姐的舊衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.65,0:16:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且尺寸正合適呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香說想要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有穿過夏季制服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.59,0:16:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等病好了以後穿上看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好色…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你露出好色的表情嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.97,0:16:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是  才沒有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一  上次照的那些相片沖洗好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:17:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  差不多打算拿去沖洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了的話會拿過來給你看的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後再看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等手術以後再看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.32,0:17:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那本書…已經可以看了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要仔細地看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於要開始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.68,0:17:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:18:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香現在在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要進手術室了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原來在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.76,0:18:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的飯已經給收拾掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞希子小姐  手術需要這麼久嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  還會更久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前段時間不是去過你家一次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.39,0:19:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時偷借了一張出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說相片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.32,0:19:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你笑得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.30,0:19:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像個跟屁蟲一樣抱著你爸爸的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想如果送給里香的話  她一定會很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手就不自覺地動起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香呢  一直笑瞇瞇地盯著相片看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣開心的表情  說不定是第一次見到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在笑什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼好事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.80,0:19:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香帶在了身上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.99,0:20:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝進密封的袋子裡 經過消毒後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.73,0:20:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貼在了不會妨礙到手術的右腿上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想當作護身符吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.41,0:20:16.98,back,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(432,470)}「你的精神狀態是麻木 是肉慾 還是戀愛」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:19.12,back,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(432,470)}「三者必居之一」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.34,0:20:24.22,back,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(432,470)}「在我看來 不如說你位於第三種狀態」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:27.59,back,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(432,470)}「與前兩者相比  戀愛更為適合於你」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.64,0:20:30.20,back,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(432,470)}「請原諒我這些時日的消沉」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:34.35,back,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(432,470)}「我的確還在生長變化的途中」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.30,0:20:37.08,back,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(432,470)}「吾友啊  你痛苦嗎」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.85,0:20:39.95,back,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(432,470)}「我們想得總是太多」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:46.90,back,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(432,470)}「絕不要採取卑怯的行動」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.92,0:20:50.00,back,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(432,470)}「惟有迎著暴風雨前進」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.58,0:20:52.85,back,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(432,470)}「倒不如主動前進 選擇死亡」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.61,0:20:57.06,back,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(432,470)}「我們的愛將凌駕於誹謗與恐嚇之上」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:20:59.83,back,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(432,470)}「讓我們兩人證明這點」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:02.87,back,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(432,470)}「賭上生命 為你所擁有」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.92,0:21:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.65,0:21:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「賭上生命 為你所擁有」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.77,0:21:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  你還在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.05,0:21:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.27,0:21:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.36,0:21:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.52,0:21:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.32,0:21:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太脆弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.37,0:21:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來組織就很脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:22:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為父親也是這樣  所以在預料之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查閱過文獻  制定了對策
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但情況太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.74,0:22:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對外科醫生來說這就是噩夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.42,0:22:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使用線縫上 卻又因線的壓力而崩開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.69,0:22:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這意味著什麼嗎  戎崎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.53,0:22:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像是在縫補豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的連我也是第一次見到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.01,0:22:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是場噩夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.58,0:22:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戎崎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.39,0:22:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕對你而言 將是最壞的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.38,0:24:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的只有稱為希望的謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.63,0:24:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏在那裡的是稱為絕望的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.36,0:24:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.21,0:24:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  仰望半月的夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.37,0:24:17.15,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,355)}我們的雙手…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.70,0:24:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的只有被稱作希望的騙局
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.29,0:24:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏在那裡的是被稱作絕望的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.88,0:24:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我這樣渺小的人無法改變什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.09,0:24:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我不想放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.74,0:24:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.44,0:24:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我選擇放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.24,0:24:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為的是不再放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.22,0:24:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  即便如此我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.11,0:24:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  仰望半月的夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.50,0:24:47.17,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,355)}我們的雙手…
